{"questionId":"9075076","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Yellow light from a sodium lamp of wavelength 590 nm is incident at normal incidence&nbsp;on a double slit. The resulting interference pattern is observed on a screen.&nbsp;The intensity of the pattern on the screen is shown.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"__IMG__/781241175cdb39d6ce12aca4b7cb635d901cc008.png\"></p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Calculate the separation of the two slits.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p>use of <em>s</em> =&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{\\lambda D}}{d}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>λ</mi>\n      <mi>D</mi>\n    </mrow>\n    <mi>d</mi>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span> with 3 fringes&nbsp;«<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{590 \\times {{10}^{ - 9}} \\times 7.0}}{{4.1 \\times {{10}^{ - 2}}}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>590</mn>\n      <mo>×</mo>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mrow>\n            <mn>10</mn>\n          </mrow>\n          <mrow>\n            <mo>−</mo>\n            <mn>9</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n      <mo>×</mo>\n      <mn>7.0</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>4.1</mn>\n      <mo>×</mo>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mrow>\n            <mn>10</mn>\n          </mrow>\n          <mrow>\n            <mo>−</mo>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span>»</p>\n<p>3.0 x 10<sup>–4</sup>&nbsp;«m»</p>\n<p><em>Allow ECF.</em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"9075076","referenceCode":"17N.2.HL.TZ0.a.iii","subjectId":"46-dp-physics-last-assessment-2024","title":"Calculate the separation of the two slits.","paper":"2","level":"HL","questionNumber":"a.iii","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 2]","breadcrumbLabels":["Additional higher level (AHL)","Additional higher level (AHL)","Topic